&lt;p&gt;Never got to learn Singlish in school? Well here&amp;rsquo;s your chance!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Even if you went to school in Singapore, where everyone speaks Singlish,
you never would have gotten a proper lesson, with a proper exam.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-wrapper speaker&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble speech right&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Wa lao eh, got Singlish exam, I sure score A-star in PSLE wan!&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;/div&gt;
  
    
    
    
