&lt;h3 id=&#34;answers:dd0fb1ac9e2cad3ee19eb638ca44a373&#34;&gt;Answers&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-wrapper speaker&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble speech right&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Dun cheat ah! Finish the questions first, then see the answers.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;/div&gt;
  
    
    
    
    &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-speaker right&#34;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-inner&#34;&gt;
        
          &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-image&#34;&gt;
            &lt;img src=&#34;http://shirtlah.com/images/textbubble/limpeh-right-200x200.png&#34; /&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        
        
          &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-name&#34;&gt;
            Limpeh
          &lt;/div&gt;
        
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  
  &lt;span class=&#34;clearfloats&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(1) The answer is &lt;em&gt;B&lt;/em&gt; “Ramu got 5 apples &lt;strong&gt;meh?&lt;/strong&gt;”&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Because Ramu has 2 + 3 - 1 - 1 = 3 apples. Since he has 3 apples, you are rejecting the statement that he has 5 apples, therefore &lt;strong&gt;meh?&lt;/strong&gt; is appropriate here, because you are questioning it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(2) The answers are &lt;strong&gt;in bold&lt;/strong&gt; in the full passage below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Siti asks Ramu for 1 apple &lt;strong&gt;back&lt;/strong&gt;. Ramu say &lt;strong&gt;cannot&lt;/strong&gt;. Siti &lt;strong&gt;ask&lt;/strong&gt; why &lt;strong&gt;cannot&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ramu says &amp;ldquo;&lt;strong&gt;Wa lao&lt;/strong&gt; eh, why you &lt;strong&gt;liddat&lt;/strong&gt;? Just now you gimme, then now you want &lt;strong&gt;back&lt;/strong&gt;. You super &lt;strong&gt;bo liao&lt;/strong&gt; leh!&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Siti says &amp;ldquo;I dun like this cloze passage. My &lt;strong&gt;PETS&lt;/strong&gt; text book everything &lt;strong&gt;also got&lt;/strong&gt; happy ending&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

